public class OperatingSystemImpl
extends com.ibm.ccl.soa.deploy.core.impl.CapabilityImpl
implements OperatingSystem

An implementation of the model object 'Operating System'.

The following features are implemented:

  • Fqdn
  • Hostname
  • Kernel Architecture
  • Kernel Version
  • Kernel Width
  • Locale
  • Manufacturer
  • Os Distribution
  • Os Servicepack
  • Os Type
  • Os Version
  • Time Zone
